## Key Terms

| Term | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| Fuzzing | Automated testing with many inputs |
| FUZZ | ffuf placeholder replaced by wordlist entries |
| False positive | A response that looks valid but is not |
| Filter | Removing unwanted responses from output |
| Calibrate | Auto-detect and remove false positive patterns |
| Vhost | Virtual host — multiple domains on one IP |
| Parameter | A key=value pair in a URL or POST body |
